o%20refreshing%20about%20being%20around%20people%20who%20remind%20you%20there's%20more%20to%20life%20than%20bowel%20movements%20and%20cartoons%2C%20more%20to%20talk%20about%20than%20drama%20at%20day%20care%20and%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20to%20feed%20picky%20eaters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20a%20different%20part%20of%20me%20comes%20alive%20when%20I'm%20around%20old%20friends%2C%20and%20I%20let%20myself%20get%20swept%20up%20in%20nostalgia%20or%20fall%20back%20into%20the%20rhythm%20of%20familiar%20inside%20jokes.%20In%20short%2C%20it's%20pure%2C%20easy%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20always%20easy%20to%20carve%20out%20adults-only%20time%20with%20friends%2C%20but%20it's%20always%20worth%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22850ec66f-7b6a-4541-9b6f-2d5c0b00a708%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20always%20make%20time%20for%20exercise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%2037%20and%20have%20no%20delusions%20about%20chasing%20the%20elusive%20six-pack%2C%20but%20exercise%20still%20has%20an%20important%20place%20in%20my%20life.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20very%20few%20times%20during%20the%20week%20that's%20just%20for%20me%2C%20and%20while%20I'm%20probably%20more%20likely%20to%20hurt%20myself%20than%20set%20a%20new%20personal%20record%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexercise-is-good-for-our-mental-health-but-more-is-not-always-better-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emental%20benefits%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20massive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there's%20some%20vanity%20to%20wanting%20to%20look%20my%20best%2C%20but%20I%20think%20it's%20also%20about%20wanting%20to%20stay%20attached%20to%20my%20former%20self%20%E2%80%94%20who%20would%20probably%20be%20appalled%20if%20he%20knew%20when%20the%20last%20time%20was%20that%20I%20bought%20myself%20clothes%20or%20had%20a%20long%2C%20relaxing%20shower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229824d44e-cb1b-4b23-9d7c-932b50276731%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMusic%20and%20hobbies%20remind%20me%20I%20have%20my%20own%20interests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spend%20so%20much%20time%20listening%20to%20music%20with%20my%20kids%20that%20my%20own%20tastes%20can%20get%20swallowed%20up.%20There's%20the%20obvious%20stuff%20that%20I%20can't%20wait%20to%20turn%20off%20once%20they're%20out%20of%20the%20car%2C%20like%20Doc%20McStuffins%20jingles%20(though%2C%20I%20admit%2C%20they're%20catchy).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%20there's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccident-broken-collarbone-ribs-europe-taylor-swift-eras-tour-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20we%20all%20love.%20But%20that's%20not%20really%20%3Cem%3Emy%20%3C%2Fem%3Emusic%2C%20it's%20a%20shared%20interest%20with%20my%20girls.%20I%20have%20to%20proactively%20remember%20to%20put%20on%20stuff%20that's%20only%20for%20me%20(2000s%20pop-punk%2C%20for%20the%20record)%20with%20no%20hope%20that%20anyone%20else%20in%20the%20family%20will%20like%20it%20(they%20won't)%2C%20because%20it's%20purely%20for%20my%20own%20enjoyment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHobbies%3F%20Most%20parents%20I%20know%20have%20forgotten%20what%20a%20hobby%20is.%20But%20I%20pick%20them%20up%20frequently%2C%20even%20if%20they%20usually%20fall%20by%20the%20wayside%20quickly.%20What's%20important%20to%20me%20is%20that%20I%20keep%20trying%2C%20whether%20re-downloading%20that%20Chess%20app%20or%20dusting%20off%20my%20acoustic%20guitar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20don't%20stay%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-find-hobbies-connect-find-creativity-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterested%20in%20the%20same%20hobby%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20long%2C%20but%20I%20like%20to%20give%20myself%20permission%20to%20pursue%20one%20when%20the%20itch%20strikes%20and%20the%20schedule%20loosens%20up.%20I%20don't%20feel%20guilty%20for%20wasting%20time%20on%20it%20or%20abandoning%20it%20once%20again%2C%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f9d719e3-515f-4fcc-82b4-c0e7b7dbdd55%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnowing%20how%20to%20be%20your%20own%20person%20doesn't%20make%20it%20easy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rarely%20seem%20to%20have%20enough%20time%20or%20mental%20energy%20for%20these%20things%2C%20even%20though%20I%20know%20they're%20worthwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20of%20course%2C%20most%20of%20the%20solo%20time%20I%20do%20get%20often%20comes%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20my%20wife%2C%20who%20has%20to%20work%20double-time%20in%20my%20absence.%20I%20do%20the%20same%20for%20her%20so%20she%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoga-classes-solo-travel-mindfulness-culture-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego%20to%20yoga%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20weekends%20or%20catch%20up%20with%20friends.%20These%20quid%20pro%20quos%20work%20great%2C%20but%20they%20make%20it%20almost%20impossible%20for%20us%20to%20get%20quality%20time%20together.%20And%2C%20crucially%2C%20that's%20probably%20the%20most%20important%20area%20of%20our%20pre-kid%20life%20we%20want%20to%20cling%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20so%20important%20to%20both%20of%20us%20that%20we%20see%20each%20other%20as%20more%20than%20just%20%26quot%3Bmom%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bdad.%26quot%3B%20That's%20a%20battle%20we're%20always%20fighting%2C%20but%20at%20least%20we're%20fighting%20it%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20it's%20essential%20to%20feel%20like%20I'm%20my%20own%20person%20and%20not%20just%20an%20automaton%20whose%20sole%20mission%20is%20to%20provide%20meals%20and%20entertainment%20to%20my%20children.%20Doing%20things%20just%20for%20me%20makes%20me%20a%20happier%20human%2C%20and%20being%20a%20happier%20human%20will%20%E2%80%94%20hopefully%20%E2%80%94%20make%20me%20a%20better%20parent%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmaintaining-identity-after-becoming-dad-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3