20found%20a%20way%20to%20downsize%20by%20building%20an%20ADU%20in%20her%20son's%20backyard.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMissoula's%20reformed%20zoning%20laws%20and%20state-level%20housing%20reforms%20support%20more%20ADU%20construction.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sylvia%20and%20her%20husband%20found%20out%20they%20were%20welcoming%20their%20first%20grandchild%20in%202018%2C%20the%20retired%20couple%20decided%20they%20would%20move%20from%20Arizona%20to%20live%20near%20their%20son%20and%20daughter-in-law%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-10-states-people-are-moving-to-montana-vermont-idaho-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20Missoula%2C%20Montana%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%202019%2C%20they%20relocated%20to%20a%20four-bedroom%20house%20around%20the%20corner%20from%20their%20then-one-year-old%20grandson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20Sylvia%2C%20who%20was%20a%20city%20government%20administrative%20assistant%20in%20California%20before%20she%20retired%2C%20has%20felt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-prices-montana-retired-boomer-homeowners-losing-houses-insurance-taxes-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancially%20stressed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Her%20husband%20got%20sick%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20after%20the%20couple%20moved%20to%20Montana%2C%20and%20he%20died%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20her%20house%20is%20paid%20off%2C%20her%20home-related%20costs%2C%20including%20insurance%2C%20property%20taxes%2C%20and%20maintenance%2C%20have%20risen.%20In%202019%2C%20her%20home%20insurance%20cost%20about%20%24890%2C%20but%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20her%20record-keeping%2C%20she%20paid%20almost%20%241%2C500.%20She's%20also%20felt%20squeezed%20by%20general%20inflation%2C%20including%20rising%20grocery%20costs.%20Plus%2C%20the%203%2C000-square-foot%20house%20is%20just%20too%20big%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOwning%20my%20home%20is%20going%20to%20drive%20me%20to%20the%20poor%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sylvia%2C%20who's%2071%20and%20requested%20her%20last%20name%20be%20omitted%20to%20protect%20her%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20last%20year%2C%20her%20son%20and%20daughter-in-law%20came%20to%20her%20with%20an%20idea%3A%20she%20could%20build%20and%20relocate%20to%20an%20accessory%20dwelling%20unit%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0a%20small%20detached%20home%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0in%20their%20backyard.%20The%20ADU%20would%20likely%20cost%20less%20to%20build%20than%20it%20would%20to%20buy%20another%20home%20in%20the%20neighborhood%2C%20they%20reasoned.%20And%20it%20would%20allow%20Sylvia%20to%20live%20in%20a%20smaller%2C%20accessible%20home%20very%20close%20to%20family%20as%20she%20grows%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESylvia%20talked%20with%20her%20other%20two%20kids%2C%20and%20they%20all%20agreed%20it%20was%20a%20good%20idea.%20So%20they%20found%20an%20architect%20and%20a%20contractor%2C%20and%20Sylvia%20signed%20a%20contract%20to%20pay%20%24274%2C000%20for%20the%20construction%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20viewed%20by%20BI.%20The%20600-square-foot%20one-bedroom%20home%20will%20have%20a%20vaulted%20ceiling%2C%20a%20big%20front%20porch%2C%20and%20a%20back%20deck.%20It'll%20be%20painted%20to%20match%20her%20son's%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20be%20real%20pretty%2C%26quot%3B%20Sylvia%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20hoping%20it's%20the%20last%20place%20I%20live.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20planning%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20ADU%20in%20cash%2C%20and%20the%20contractors%20are%20on%20track%20to%20complete%20it%20by%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESylvia%20plans%20to%20sell%20her%20current%20house%2C%20which%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20bought%20for%20%24315%2C000%20in%202019.%20According%20to%20documents%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-supporting-republican-montana-governor-yimby-housing-policies-lowering-rent-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehome%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20soared%20across%20Montana%2C%20the%20home%20is%20now%20valued%20at%20%24718%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EADUs%20%E2%80%94%20often%20called%20%26quot%3Bgranny%20flats%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bcasitas%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20are%20a%20particularly%20useful%20form%20of%20housing%20for%20older%20people%20who%20want%20to%20downsize%20into%20a%20smaller%2C%20more%20accessible%20home%20and%20also%20want%20to%20be%20close%20to%20family.%20Increasingly%2C%20cities%20and%20states%20across%20the%20country%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyimbys-winning-lower-house-prices-rents-build-more-homes-neighborhoods-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegalizing%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-york-city-funding-adu-tiny-homehousing-shortage-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincentivizing%3C%2Fa%3E%20ADU%20construction%20as%20a%20way%20to%20boost%20the%20supply%20of%20smaller%2C%20more%20affordable%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20the%20most%20viable%20option%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Sylvia%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20I%20would%20be%20able%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20for%20%24274%2C000.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20rendering%20of%20an%20ADU%20being%20constructed%20in%20Missoula%2C%20Montana.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669153788893442a51561f95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22483%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendering%20of%20Sylvia's%20single-story%2C%20600-square-foot%20ADU%20under%20construction%20in%20Missoula%2C%20Montana.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sylvia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b5831c72-600f-47b0-a865-ecceda5008bd%5C%22%3EADUs%20as%20a%20solution%20for%20cash-strapped%20older%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESylvia's%20ADU%20might%20not%20have%20been%20legal%20in%20Missoula%20until%20about%20a%20decade%20ago%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20it%20still%20isn't%20legal%20in%20many%20American%20residential%20neighborhoods.%20Even%20in%20states%20that%20encourage%20tiny%20home%20construction%2C%20local%20anti-development%20groups%20and%20policymakers%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmalibu-suing-homeowners-california-supreme-court-backyard-tiny-home-adu-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emake%20it%20all%20but%20impossible%20to%20build%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20backyard%20ADU.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20western%20Montana%20city%20first%20took%20action%20to%20encourage%20the%20construction%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.montanarightnow.com%2Fnews%2Fmissoula-to-adopt-adu-ordinance%2Farticle_8720276d-95b8-56cd-82e8-991fd0fcaeed.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EADUs%20in%202013%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20further%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmissoulacurrent.com%2Fregulations-adu-rules%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eloosened%20restrictions%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202020%20after%20just%2030%20ADUs%20had%20reportedly%20been%20built%20in%20the%20city.%20As%20part%20of%20broader%20zoning%20code%20reforms%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmissoulian.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Fgovernment-politics%2Fmissoula-city-coding-john-engen-zoning-mobile-homes%2Farticle_41ddb802-eb04-11ee-a8d9-6f8d560ce1d6.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecity%20council%20this%20year%20agreed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20increase%20the%20allowable%20size%20of%20ADUs%20and%20liberalize%20a%20few%20other%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20also%20pushed%20for%20more%20of%20these%20homes%20as%20part%20of%20its%20broader%20housing%20reform%20effort%20aimed%20at%20boosting%20supply.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20Montana%20state%20legislature%20passed%20a%20bipartisan%20law%20requiring%20all%20cities%20and%20towns%20to%20allow%20the%20construction%20of%20ADUs%20on%20single-family%20lots.%20But%20before%20the%20law%20went%20into%20effect%20in%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ktvh.com%2Fnews%2Fjudge-puts-hold-on-montana-zoning-related-laws%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20judge%20temporarily%20blocked%20the%20measure%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20several%20other%20pro-housing%20laws.%20The%20court%20sided%20with%20an%20organization%20of%20Montana%20homeowners%20who%20argued%20denser%20housing%20would%20alter%20the%20character%20of%20their%20neighborhoods.%20The%20state%20appealed%20the%20decision%20to%20the%20state%20supreme%20court%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221279%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20foundation%20for%20an%20accessory%20dwelling%20unit%20in%20Missoula%2C%20Montana.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669142b95439fb59cebcd72a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22713%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20foundation%20for%20Sylvia's%20ADU%20is%20under%20construction%20in%20her%20son's%20backyard.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sylvia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20as%20older%20people%2C%20including%20homeowners%2C%20are%20struggling%20with%20rising%20housing%20costs%20in%20communities%20across%20the%20country.%20Insurance%20costs%20have%20risen%20dramatically%20all%20over%20%E2%80%94%20a%20result%20of%20both%20increasingly%20severe%20climate%20issues%2C%20including%20flooding%20and%20fires%2C%20and%20the%20elevated%20cost%20of%20home%20construction%20and%20repairs.%20Nationally%2C%20home%20insurance%20premiums%20rose%20by%20an%20average%20of%2021%25%20between%20May%202022%20and%20May%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.policygenius.com%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fhome-insurance-pricing-report-2023%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHomeowners%2520insurance%2520premiums%2520in%2520the%2Cactive%2520policies%2520quoted%2520for%2520renewal.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EPolicygenius%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%20Home%20repairs%20are%20also%20more%20costly%20these%20days%2C%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-crisis-national-shortage-construction-workers-job-demand-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eshortage%20of%20construction%20workers%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.constructiondive.com%2Fnews%2Ffalling-material-prices-expected-reverse-course%2F651744%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eelevated%20cost%20of%20materials%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20portion%20of%20homeowners%2055%20and%20older%20who%20are%20cost-burdened%20%E2%80%94%20or%20spend%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20their%20income%20on%20housing%20and%20utilities%20%E2%80%94%20rose%20from%2030%25%20in%202001%20to%2045%25%20in%202022%2C%20a%20new%20report%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jchs.harvard.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Freports%2Ffiles%2FHarvard_JCHS_The_State_of_the_Nations_Housing_2024.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EHarvard%20Joint%20Center%20for%20Housing%20Studies%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20state%20of%20US%20housing%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Montana%2C%20a%20severe%20housing%20shortage%20has%20caused%20home%20prices%20to%20soar.%20But%20property%20taxes%20and%20insurance%20costs%20are%20also%20way%20up%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20many%20homeowners%20to%20afford%20their%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElderly%20and%20disabled%20people%20are%20struggling%20really%2C%20really%20hard%2C%26quot%3B%20Beverly%20Dashnaw%2C%20a%20HUD-certified%20housing%20counselor%20in%20Helena%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-prices-montana-retired-boomer-homeowners-losing-houses-insurance-taxes-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThe%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20inflation%20is%20going%20up%20for%20everything%2C%20and%20their%20income%20doesn't%20go%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESylvia%20is%20lucky%20she%20can%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20her%20home's%20market%20value%20without%20having%20to%20buy%20another%20home%20in%20an%20impossible%20market%20with%20high%20interest%20rates.%20And%20Missoula%20has%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20good%20place%20to%20age%2C%20she%20says.%20If%20she%20can't%20drive%2C%20she%20can%20take%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmountainline.com%2Fsustainability%2Fzero-fare%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMountain%2520Line%2520operates%2520a%2520zero%2Chave%2520to%2520pay%2520to%2520ride.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecity's%20free%20buses%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20library%2C%20where%20she%20volunteers%20each%20week%2C%20and%20to%20the%20pickleball%20courts%2C%20where%20she%20plays%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20small%20town%2C%20I%20love%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20easy%20to%20get%20around%2C%20and%20I%20know%20my%20way%20around.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20homeowner%20struggling%20with%20rising%20insurance%20premiums%20or%20other%20costs%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aerelman%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eerelman%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-housing-costs-cheaper-tiny-house-adu-montana-law-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721121842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669569408893442a5156b365%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-housing-costs-cheaper-tiny-house-adu-montana-law-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sylvia%2C%20a%2071-year-old%20retiree%20in%20Montana%2C%20is%20taking%20advantage%20of%20city%20and%20state%20laws%20encouraging%20the%20construction%20of%20accessory%20dwelling%20units.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Eliza%20Relman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-housing-costs-cheaper-tiny-house-adu-montana-law-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Gets%202%20New%20Judges%2C%20Including%20First%20From%20Manipur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20now%20has%20two%20more%20judges%20after%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20cleared%20the%20appointments%20of%20Justice%20N%20Kotiswar%20Singh%20and%20Justice%20R%20Mahadevan.%C2%A0The%20appointments%20were%20announced%20by%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20Collegium%20had%20earlier%20recommended%20the%20elevation%20of%20these%20two%20judges.%20With%20these%20two%20appointments%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20its%20sanctioned%20strength%20of%2034%20judges%2C%20including%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20exercise%20of%20the%20powers%20conferred%20by%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%2C%20Hon'ble%20President%2C%20after%20consultation%20with%20Hon'ble%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%2C%20is%20pleased%20to%20appoint%20the%20following%20as%3Cbr%3E%5CnSupreme%20Court%20Judges%3A-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOWQ9iGIooG%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOWQ9iGIooG%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20(%40arjunrammeghwal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Farjunrammeghwal%2Fstatus%2F1813115139920425067%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20N%20Kotiswar%20Singh%C2%A0is%20the%20first%20judge%20from%20Manipur%20to%20be%20elevated%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20He%20is%20currently%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20Ladakh.%20Justice%20Singh%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Manipur's%20first%20Advocate%20General%20N%20Ibotombi%20Singh.%20An%20alumnus%20of%20Kirori%20Mal%20College%20and%20Campus%20Law%20Centre%2C%20Delhi%20University%2C%20he%20started%20is%20career%20as%20an%20advocate%20in%201986.%20He%20has%20also%20served%20as%20Manipur%20Advocate%20General%20before%20he%20became%20a%20judge.%20He%20has%20served%20in%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20and%20Manipur%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Mahadevan%20is%20currently%20the%20acting%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20Madras%20High%20Court.%20Born%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Justice%20Mahadevan%20is%20an%20alumnus%20of%20Madras%20Law%20College.%20As%20a%20lawyer%2C%20he%20has%20appeared%20in%20over%209%2C000%20cases%20and%20has%20also%20served%20as%20Additional%20Government%20Pleader%20(taxes)%20for%20the%20Government%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Additional%20Central%20Government%20Standing%20Counsel%20and%20Senior%20Panel%20Counsel%20for%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20at%20Madras%20High%20Court.%20He%20was%20elevated%20as%20a%20judge%20of%20Madras%20High%20Court%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721121780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F6611la2o_supreme-court-new-judges_625x300_16_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjustice-n-kotiswar-singh-justice-r-mahadevan-supreme-court-gets-2-new-judges-its-first-from-manipur-6117032%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20now%20has%20two%20more%20judges%20after%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20cleared%20the%20appointments%20of%20Justice%20N%20Kotiswar%20Singhand%20Justice%20R%20Mahadevan.%20The%20appointments%20were%20announced%20by%20Law%20Minister%20Arjun%20Ram%20Meghwal%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww