p%3ECurio%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHera%20Wentong%20Li%20left%20a%20lucrative%20tech%20career%20to%20start%20Curio%2C%20a%20book%20subscription%20for%20bilingual%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20stints%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Slack%2C%20she%20realized%20her%20career%20was%20unfulfilling.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20has%20no%20regrets%20but%20says%20she%20does%20miss%20solving%20abstract%20and%20challenging%20tech%20problems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Hera%20Wentong%20Li%2C%20the%2036-year-old%20founder%20of%20Curio%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20born%20in%20Singapore%20and%20raised%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraised-bilingual-grateful-family-communication-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebilingual%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%20speaking%20both%20English%20and%20Mandarin.%20I%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20in%202006%20to%20study%20computer%20engineering%20at%20Cornell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%2013-year%20tech%20career%2C%20I%20founded%20Curio%2C%20a%20subscription%20book%20club%20that%20fosters%20bilingual%20learning%20in%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%20my%20career%2C%20I%20held%20positions%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-job-morgan-stanley-startup-founder-loneliness-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMorgan%20Stanley%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Redi%20Technologies%2C%20and%20Amazon.%20I%20then%20worked%20at%20a%20startup%20and%20AppNexus%20before%20becoming%20the%20senior%20engineering%20manager%20and%20head%20of%20search%20engineering%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-brand-deals-ugc-slack-user-generated-content-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESlack%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20salary%20at%20Slack%20was%20%24230%2C000%2C%20but%20I%20had%20over%20%24500%2C000%20in%20equity%20annually%20(depending%20on%20the%20stock%20price%20and%20my%20bonus)%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20years%2C%20I%20took%20home%20seven%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22209c47c4-539e-4648-91d3-eae27d1c69d7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20led%20the%20search%20engineering%20team%2C%20overseeing%20more%20than%2020%20engineers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wore%20many%20hats%20at%20Slack%2C%20managing%20projects%20across%20different%20tech%20stacks%2C%20hiring%20and%20onboarding%20engineers%2C%20and%20planning%20for%20future%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20prioritized%20the%20impact%20of%20my%20work%20and%20the%20people%20I%20worked%20with.%20In%20my%20early%20years%2C%20we%20grew%20rapidly%2C%20I%20loved%20my%20job%2C%20and%20the%20high%20salary%20was%20a%20nice%20bonus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20the%20growth%20plateaued%2C%20my%20role%20became%20less%20impactful%20and%20focused%20more%20on%20organizational%20management%20than%20creation.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20building%20an%20app%20or%20trading%20platform%20no%20longer%20fulfilled%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227143d234-09d9-476e-a2ea-91929903ea5f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBecoming%20a%20mother%20brought%20new%20challenges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pandemic%20hit%20when%20I%20was%20a%20new%20mom.%20As%20the%20world%20grappled%20with%20conflicts%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhate-incidents-against-asian-americans-have-skyrocketed-2021-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eracial%20divisions%2C%20and%20hate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20wrestling%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20guilt%20%E2%80%94%20what%20had%20I%20brought%20my%20daughter%20into%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20thinking%20often%20about%20how%20best%20to%20prepare%20the%20next%20generation.%20How%20can%20we%20steer%20them%20away%20from%20endless%20scrolling%20and%20instead%20cultivate%20empathy%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20determination%20in%20them%3F%20I%20also%20started%20thinking%20about%20instilling%20my%20unique%20cultural%20heritage%20into%20my%20children%20and%20raising%20them%20to%20be%20true%20to%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReading%20is%20a%20cherished%20pastime%20for%20my%20family%2C%20but%20I%20struggled%20to%20find%20quality%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclassic-best-childrens-books-2017-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildren's%20books%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Chinese.%20Reflecting%20on%20my%20upbringing%20in%20Singapore%2C%20where%20books%20were%20a%20cornerstone%20of%20my%20childhood%2C%20I%20realized%20their%20immense%20impact%20on%20shaping%20my%20imagination%20and%20broadening%20my%20horizons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20couldn't%20ignore%20the%20lack%20of%20resources%20for%20bilingual%20education%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20which%20seemed%20absurd%20in%20this%20era%20of%20limitless%20internet%20accessibility.%20A%20spark%20ignited%20within%20me%2C%20and%20this%20realization%20birthed%20the%20idea%20of%20Curio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dac0db09-8916-4d4f-ba02-dc8b650344ac%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20had%20some%20anxiety%20about%20leaving%20a%20successful%2013-year%20career%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20nervous%20but%20felt%20I%20was%20in%20the%20right%20place%20to%20take%20on%20the%20challenge%20of%20starting%20a%20business.%20I%20waited%20until%20I%20had%20enough%20savings%20and%20enough%20vested%20equity%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-big-tech-dream-job-pay-perks-not-worth-it-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20quit%3C%2Fa%3E.%20My%20main%20concern%20stemmed%20from%20leaving%20a%20tech%20career%20with%20lots%20of%20potential%20and%20growth%20and%20the%20uncertainty%20of%20whether%20it%20would%20be%20easy%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20quit%2C%20I%20spent%20six%20months%20doing%20market%20research%2C%20competitive%20analysis%2C%20and%20talking%20to%20various%20founders%20and%20publishers%2C%20which%20helped%20to%20minimize%20my%20uncertainty.%20I%20scheduled%20a%20few%20meetings%20each%20week%20and%20attended%20networking%20events%20after%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20immense%20joy%20in%20connecting%20with%20educators%20and%20moms%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2276369ade-bd0c-4652-987b-9ec6fcdafb51%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECurio%20was%20bootstrapped%20with%20my%20own%20funds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20invested%20around%20%24200%2C000%20in%20the%20first%20year%20to%20get%20Curio%20off%20the%20ground.%20We%20officially%20launched%20in%20April%202023.%20A%20friend%20of%20mine%2C%20Kimberly%20Atiyeh%2C%20who%20has%20a%20background%20in%20linguistics%20and%20marketing%2C%20came%20on%20as%20head%20of%20growth%20in%20February%202023%2C%20helping%20launch%20our%20French%20subscription.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20we%20did%20everything%20ourselves%2C%20including%20packing%20orders%20and%20handling%20customer%20service.%20This%20gave%20us%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20every%20aspect%20of%20the%20business%2C%20which%20has%20helped%20us%20streamline%20and%20scale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20running%20the%20business%2C%20we're%20also%20always%20working%20on%20the%20next%20product%20in%20all%20four%20languages%20(currently%2C%20we%20offer%20Spanish%2C%20French%2C%20traditional%20Chinese%2C%20and%20simplified%20Chinese).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKimberly%20and%20I%20now%20have%20two%20toddlers%20each%20with%20full%20social%20and%20sickness%20calendars.%20Balancing%20all%20of%20this%20has%20been%20our%20biggest%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ce8b854-0257-4716-a156-25fa226b640c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20work%20more%20hours%20than%20I%20did%20at%20Slack%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdream-job-in-office-work-full-time-flexibility-benefits-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20flexibility%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20at%20Slack%2C%20but%20my%20working%20hours%20are%20longer.%20Most%20weeks%2C%20I%20wake%20up%20early%20at%205%20a.m.%20to%20finish%20some%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20breakfast%20and%20school%20drop-off%2C%20I%20get%20back%20to%20work.%20Some%20days%2C%20I%20spend%20hours%20refining%20the%20website%20to%20improve%20conversions%20or%20develop%20new%20features.%20Other%20parts%20of%20the%20day%20are%20dedicated%20to%20collaborating%20with%20Kimberly%20to%20strategize%20for%20upcoming%20book%20selections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20manage%20the%20operational%20and%20logistical%20aspects%20of%20the%20business.%20The%20diverse%20facets%20of%20my%20role%20keep%20me%20engaged%20and%20invested%20in%20every%20aspect%20of%20Curio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c90ca88e-209c-4114-a637-d5ea190d71d3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20biggest%20tip%20for%20fellow%20startup%20entrepreneurs%20is%20to%20talk%20to%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETalk%20to%20fellow%20founders%20and%20investors%20during%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20exploration.%20It's%20crucial%20to%20approach%20these%20conversations%20discerningly%2C%20recognizing%20that%20not%20everyone%20knows%20your%20product%20or%20market%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20try%20to%20sell%20something%20early.%20While%20surveys%20and%20market%20research%20are%20valuable%2C%20they%20can%20be%20limited%20by%20confirmation%20biases.%20The%20most%20effective%20way%20to%20validate%20your%20ideas%20is%20by%20taking%20the%20leap%20and%20actually%20selling%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20regret%20my%20journey%2C%20but%20I%20miss%20solving%20abstract%20and%20challenging%20problems%20in%20tech.%20I'm%20not%20receiving%20any%20salary%20right%20now%20and%20don't%20expect%20to%20for%20the%20next%20few%20years.%20My%20focus%20is%20on%20continuing%20to%20grow%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-successful-tech-career-motherhood-changed-priorities-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721120702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66956d2f5439fb59cebd7be1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-successful-tech-career-motherhood-changed-priorities-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hera%20Wentong%20Li%20worked%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20at%20Morgan%20Stanley%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Slack%20before%20realizing%20she%20wasn't%20fulfilled%20by%20her%20tech%20career.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Perri%20Ormont%20Blumberg)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-successful-tech-career-motherhood-changed-priorities-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BVirat%20Didn't%20Like%20Gambhir's%20Gesture%2C%20Abused...%26quot%3B%3A%20IPL%202023%20Clash%20Truth%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202023%20campaign%20produced%20some%20fiery%20clashes%20on%20the%20field%2C%20with%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20superstar%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Virat%20Kohli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F967-virat-kohli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVirat%20Kohli%3C%2Fa%3E%20taking%20on%20Lucknow%20Super%20Giants'%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Naveen-ul-Haq%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107680-naveen-ul-haq-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENaveen-ul-Haq%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20clash%20between%20the%20two%20spiralled%20on%20beyond%20the%20match%2C%20with%20LSG%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20throwing%20himself%20in%20the%20altercation.%20Gambhir%20and%20Kohli%20had%20a%20heated%20argument%20that%20prompted%20forced%20their%20teammates%20to%20intervene.%20Now%2C%20Lucknow%20spinner%20Amit%20Mishra%20has%20revealed%20what%20exactly%20was%20the%20reason%20behind%20such%20an%20explosive%20clash%20that%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20chat%20during%20a%20podcast%20on%20YouTube%2C%20LSG's%20veteran%20spinner%20Amit%20Mishra%20revealed%20that%20the%20story%20started%20a%20few%20matches%20before%20in%20Bengaluru%20when%20Lucknow%20mentor%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20had%20done%20the%20'finger%20on%20mouth'%20gesture%20towards%20Bengaluru%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20all%20started%20in%20Bengaluru%20where%20we%20(LSG)%20won%20the%20game%20and%20Gambhir%20expressed%20his%20aggression.%20The%20public%20was%20going%20mad%20so%20Gautam%20gestured%20them%20to%20keep%20quiet.%20Probably%20Virat%20Kohli%20didn't%20like%20that.%20We%20thought%20the%20matter%20ended%20with%20the%20game%20but%20not%20for%20Kohli%2C%26quot%3B%20Mishra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%2C%20according%20to%20Mishra%2C%20was%20probably%20not%20happy%20with%20Gambhir's%20gesture%20and%20started%20to%20abuse%20LSG%20players%20when%20the%20two%20teams%20met%20again.%20Mishra%20said%20that%20Virat%20could've%20avoided%20certain%20things%20but%20he%20chose%20not%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20started%20abusing%20our%20players%20(in%20the%20LSG%20vs%20RCB%20rematch%20in%20Lucknow).%20He%20didn't%20have%20any%20grudges%20with%20Kyle%20Myers%20but%20he%20abused%20him%20as%20well.%20Naveen-ul-Haq%20was%20bowling%2C%20he%20would%20abuse%20him%20too.%20Bohot%20cheezein%20avoid%20ho%20sakti%20thi%20but%20Virat%20Kohli%20ne%20nahi%20ki%20(a%20lot%20of%20things%20would%20have%20been%20avoided%20but%20Kohli%20chose%20not%20to).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20even%20had%20an%20altercation%20with%20Mishra%20when%20he%20was%20batting%20with%20Naven%20in%20the%20middle.%20As%20Mishra%20tried%20to%20calm%20things%20down%2C%20Virat%20told%20him%20to%20explain%20the%20same%20to%20Naveen%2C%20not%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20batting%20with%20Naveen%2C%20I%20asked%20Kohli%2C%20'Who%20are%20you%20even%20talking%20to%20He's%20just%20a%20youngster%20and%20not%20even%20close%20to%20your%20stature.%20Whatever%20happened%20has%20happened.'%20He%20answered%20back%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20make%20him%20understand%20that%2C%20not%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Mishra%2C%20Virat%20didn't%20calm%20down%20even%20after%20the%20match%20concluded%20and%20continued%20to%20abuse%20Naveen%2C%20this%20is%20when%20Gambhir%20decided%20to%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20problem%20began%20after%20the%20game.%20He%20(Kohli)%20started%20abusing%20him%20again%20during%20the%20customary%20handshakes.%20That's%20when%20Gambhir%20intervened%2C%20questing%20why%20are%20you%20starting%20it%20again%20when%20the%20game%20has%20ended%20and%20you%20guys%20have%20won.%20I%20moved%20Gambhir%20away%20but%20Naveen%20later%20came%20to%20the%20dressing%20and%20said%20that%20Kohli%20started%20abusing%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kohli%20and%20Naveen%20seemed%20to%20have%20buried%20to%20hatchet%2C%20having%20played%20against%20each%20other%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20since%20the%20incident%2C%20Mishra%20doesn't%20thing%20the%20Afghanistan%20pacer%20will%20ever%20respect%20the%20Team%20India%20batter%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20social%20media%2C%20it%20all%20seemed%20to%20be%20over%20between%20them.%20But%20do%20you%20think%20Naveen%20will%20respect%20Kohli%20ever%20again%3F%20What%20about%20the%20youngsters%20who%20saw%20the%20incident%20where%20a%20big%20star%20was%20abusing%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20Mishra%20wondered.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721120700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F4sjhm84o_kohli-naveen_650x300_02_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%