0b1-b3ae-7c83026aa9f6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECoca-Cola%20is%20better%20in%20France%2C%20Dr.%20Pepper%20is%20worse%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20there%20is%20one%20thing%20all%20three%20of%20us%20agree%20on%2C%20it's%20that%2C%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20Coca-Cola%20in%20France%20is%20the%20best%20Coca-Cola%20any%20of%20us%20have%20had%20anywhere%20else%20in%20the%20world%20(so%20far).%20We%20rarely%20drink%20it%20at%20home%20in%20the%20States%20because%20it%20always%20feels%20too%20sugary%2C%20but%20in%20France%3F%20We%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-didnt-drink-soda-for-a-month-heres-what-happened-2019-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edrinking%20Coke%20multiple%20times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20a%20week.%20There%20is%20something%20so%20refreshing%2C%20so%20very%20nearly%20clean%20about%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDon't%20get%20me%20wrong%3A%20I%20am%20pretty%20sure%20that%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20Coke%20in%20France%20isn't%20any%20better%20for%20us%20than%20it%20is%20in%20the%20US.%20But%20I%20do%20know%20that%20one%20of%20the%20things%20we%20talk%20about%20before%20we%20head%20over%2C%20while%20we're%20on%20the%20flight%2C%20and%20again%20as%20we%20are%20getting%20on%20the%20train%20or%20settling%20into%20our%20first%20Uber%20after%20arriving%2C%20is%20sitting%20down%20at%20a%20caf%C3%A9%20and%20enjoying%20a%20glass%20of%20Coke.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3d6993c-46f1-4479-99c0-5779c77cef92%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGas%20stations%20in%20France%20are%20better%20than%20those%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20summer%20is%20the%20first%20one%20we've%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frent-a-car-cheap-alternatives-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erented%20a%20car%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20spent%20significant%20time%20driving%20throughout%20France.%20We%20typically%20stay%20in%20Cannes%20and%20Paris%20and%20often%20fly%20or%20take%20the%20train%20between%20the%20two.%20This%20experience%20has%20come%20with%20a%20startling%20experience%3A%20Shell%20gas%20stations%20in%20France%20are%20wildly%20more%20clean%20and%20comfortable%20than%20they%20are%20in%20the%20States%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20they're%20even%20borderline%20beautiful.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20sure%20I%20can't%20speak%20for%20every%20Shell%20station%20in%20America%2C%20but%20by%20and%20large%2C%20the%20ones%20I%20have%20frequented%20are%20small%20and%20usually%20dirty%2C%20and%20you're%20lucky%20if%20there's%20more%20than%20one%20restroom%20stall.%20To%20contrast%20this%2C%20we've%20encountered%20Shell%20stations%20that%20boast%20not%20one%2C%20not%20two%2C%20but%20three%20separate%20restaurants%20or%20caf%C3%A9s%2C%20Starbucks%20coffee%20stations%2C%20bookstores%2C%20the%20cleanest%20gas%20station%20restrooms%20with%20at%20least%2010%20stalls%2C%20and%20dining%20areas%20that%20can%20hold%20around%2030%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e925462-4eb3-4b51-9635-9ca618aa0fed%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20can%20buy%20one%20water%20bottle%20out%20of%20the%20package%20(instead%20of%20buying%20the%20whole%20thing)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20favorite%20fact%20about%20France%20is%20that%20when%20purchasing%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-water-bottle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebottled%20water%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(which%20is%20super%20popular%20in%20the%20country%20even%20though%20tap%20water%20is%20totally%20safe)%2C%20you%20can%20rip%20open%20the%20plastic%20packaging%20that%20encases%2012%20bottles%20and%20just%20remove%20one%20%E2%80%94%20and%20you%20can%20buy%20just%20that%20one.%20This%20never%20ceases%20to%20amaze%20my%20kid%2C%20who%20has%20threatened%20to%20attempt%20the%20same%20feat%20in%20the%20US%20(though%20I%20have%20a%20feeling%20the%20reception%20would%20be%E2%80%A6%20less%20than%20great).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d8d435f9-7328-4149-b5b9-8c57cfd7b4ec%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20roads%20are%20tiny%20%E2%80%94%20even%20the%20interstates%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20difference%20that%20always%20seems%20to%20catch%20my%20son%20by%20surprise%20is%20just%20how%20narrow%20the%20roads%20in%20many%20French%20cities%20really%20are.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdifference-driving-in-the-us-and-france-2016-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EDriving%20in%20France%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20always%20a%20fascinating%20experience%20(or%2C%20I%20should%20say%2C%20being%20a%20passenger%20while%20my%20partner%20drives)%20primarily%20because%20it%20constantly%20feels%20like%20you're%20going%20to%20slam%20into%20the%20car%20next%20to%20you%2C%20or%20the%20sharply%20angled%2C%20very%20thin%20descent%20into%20a%20parking%20garage%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20last%20one%20you'll%20ever%20make.%20We%20always%20wonder%20what%20it%20feels%20like%20for%20the%20French%20to%20drive%20in%20the%20US%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20with%20our%20massive%20highway%20lanes%20and%20monster%20vehicles.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d1f0aec-0d6f-4062-b304-21833241843b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20Taco%20Bell%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20is%20no%20greater%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-surprised-my-welsh-kids-when-they-visited-the-us-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esurprise%20my%20son%20has%20experienced%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20France%20than%20this%3A%20the%20country%20is%20not%20home%20to%20any%20Taco%20Bells%2C%20or%20at%20least%20none%20that%20we've%20ever%20been%20able%20to%20find.%20In%20addition%20to%20just%20flat-out%20being%20my%20favorite%20fast%20food%2C%20Taco%20Bell%20is%20also%20a%20favorite%20of%20my%20son's%20because%20he's%20been%20a%20vegetarian%20his%20entire%20life%2C%20and%20you%20can%20always%20count%20on%20Taco%20Bell%20for%20a%20few%20bean%20burritos%20(no%20red%20sauce%2C%20no%20onions)%20in%20a%20pinch.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reason%20for%20the%20lack%20of%20Taco%20Bell%20has%20never%20been%20explained%20to%20me%2C%20and%20France%20clearly%20has%20no%20problem%20hosting%20fast%20food%20establishments%20from%20the%20US%20(KFC%2C%20McDonald's%2C%20and%20Burger%20King%20are%20everywhere).%20To%20say%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20Taco%20Bell%20has%20made%20some%20days%20harder%20than%20others%20is%20an%20understatement%2C%20and%20we%20both%20remain%20hopeful%20that%20one%20day%20someone%2C%20somewhere%2C%20will%20franchise%20it%20throughout%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3Eother%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20red%2C%20white%2C%20and%20blue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-kid-noticed-differences-between-france-us-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721120522000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66955ac78893442a5156ad71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-kid-noticed-differences-between-france-us-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20American%20son%20spends%20half%20the%20year%20in%20France%20and%20half%20in%20the%20US.%20He%20noticed%20roads%20are%20smaller%20in%20France%2C%20and%20Coca-Cola%20is%20better%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Stephanie%20Kaloi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-kid-noticed-differences-between-france-us-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Biden%20announces%20plan%20to%20cap%20rent%20increases%20at%205%25%20for%20half%20of%20American%20rental%20households%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225436%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Biden%20stands%20on%20a%20military%20tarmac%20in%20front%20of%20a%20row%20of%20microphones%20and%20reporters.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6695be0c9caa6ed01e01dde7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223496%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBiden%20answers%20reporters'%20questions%20at%20at%20Joint%20Base%20Andrews%20in%20Maryland%20ahead%20of%20his%20trip%20to%20Nevada.%3Cp%3EKENT%20NISHIMURA%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJoe%20Biden%20announced%20a%20proposal%20to%20cap%20annual%20rent%20increases%20at%205%25%20for%20the%20next%20two%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20plan%20targets%20corporate%20landlords%20with%20more%20than%2050%20units%2C%20which%20make%20up%20nearly%20half%20of%20rentals%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20the%20proposal%20would%20first%20need%20to%20pass%20a%20divided%20Congress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eon%20Tuesday%20rolled%20out%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ea%20plan%20offering%20landlords%20a%20choice%3A%20cap%20annual%20rent%20increases%20at%205%25%20for%20the%20next%20two%20years%20or%20risk%20losing%20valuable%20tax%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20proposal%20would%20apply%20to%20corporate%20landlords%2C%20defined%20as%20those%20who%20own%20more%20than%2050%20units.%20These%20landlords%20control%20more%20than%20half%20the%20national%20rental%20market%2C%20according%20to%20senior%20White%20House%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorporate%20landlords%20who%20increase%20rent%20by%20more%20than%205%25%20would%20lose%20the%20valuable%20tax%20benefit%20known%20as%20depreciation%20deductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstitutional%20investors%20are%20buying%20up%20homes%20with%20cash%2C%20turning%20them%20into%20rentals%20and%20raising%20rents%2C%26quot%3B%20White%20House%20official%20Lael%20Brainard%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpecial%20exceptions%20would%20also%20apply%20to%20units%20that%20are%20new%20construction%20or%20have%20undergone%20significant%20rehabilitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ewill%20announce%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20plan%20during%20a%20speech%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20Nevada%2C%20a%20swing%20state%20that%20has%20faced%20some%20of%20the%20steepest%20housing%20cost%20increases%20in%20the%20country.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20plan%2C%20he%20will%20also%20announce%20new%20and%20proposed%20sales%20of%20federal%20land%20in%20Nevada%20earmarked%20for%20affordable%20housing%2C%20including%2020%20acres%20near%20Clark%20County%20and%2018%20acres%20near%20Henderson%2C%20Nevada.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20rent%20cap%20proposal%20is%20essentially%20a%20campaign%20promise.%20It%20would%20first%20need%20to%20pass%20both%20chambers%20of%20Congress%2C%20which%20doesn't%20seem%20likely%20before%20the%20November%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden's%20announcement%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20a%20turbulent%20few%20weeks%20in%20the%20campaign%2C%20which%20saw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-shot-dead-if-he-did-not-tilt-head-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20failed%20assassination%20attempt%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20calls%20from%20his%20own%20party%20for%20President%20Biden%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdemocratic-donors-withholding-10s-of-millions-unless-biden-drops-out-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estep%20down%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstephen-colbert-joe-biden-debated-like-abraham-lincoln-dug-up-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshaky%20debate%20performance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20also%20comes%20as%20communities%20across%20the%20country%20face%20a%20severe%20housing%20affordability%20crisis%20caused%20largely%20by%20a%20steep%20shortage%20of%20homes.%20Renters%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-crisis-unaffordable-high-rent-prices-cost-burdened-renters-cities-2024-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DHalf%2520of%2520all%2520tenant%2520households%2Cthis%2520data%252C%2520the%2520report%2520noted.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20are%20particularly%20hard%20hit.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rents%20across%20the%20country%20have%20risen%20by%2026%25%20since%20early%202020%2C%20according%20to%20a%20recent%20report%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jchs.harvard.edu%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Freports%2Ffiles%2FHarvard_JCHS_The_State_of_the_Nations_Housing_2024.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHarvard%20Joint%20Center%20for%20Housing%20Studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20state%20of%20US%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHalf%20of%20all%20tenant%20households%20were%20cost-burdened%20as%20of%202022%2C%20meaning%20they%20spent%20more%20than%2030%25%20of%20their%20income%20on%20rent%2C%20the%20Harvard%20report%20found.%20That%20was%20the%20highest%20share%20since%20the%20US%20Census%20first%20started%20collecting%20this%20data%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%20Meanwhile%2C%20moving%20from%20renting%20to%20owning%20a%20home%20has%20also%20gotten%20much%20harder.%20Less%20than%2015%25%20of%20renter%20households%20can%20afford%20the%20monthly%20median%20payment%20for%20a%20median-priced%20home%20after%20taxes%20and%20insurance%2C%20Harvard%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20evidence%20that%20many%20landlords%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20high%20demand%20and%20a%20supply%20shortage%20to%20raise%20rents%20far%20beyond%20their%20own%20cost%20increases.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.propublica.org%2Farticle%2Fyieldstar-rent-increase-realpage-rent%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslew%20of%20corporate%20landlords%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20used%20rent-setting%20algorithmic%20software%20to%20artificially%20inflate%20rents.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-apartment-rent-price-setting-landlords-realpage-lawsuit-illegal-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%20sued%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20alledgedly%20colluding%20to%20set%20rent%20prices%20above%20competitive%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20there's%20hope%3A%20A%20near-record%20number%20of%20new%20multi-family%20rental%20units%20are%20hitting%20the%20market%2C%20and%20rents%20for%20studios%20and%20one-bedroom%20apartments%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-crisis-apartment-rent-falling-developers-building-homes-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20recently%20fallen%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225ce2735f-eb1e-4e57-bc12-a20959916f17%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20focus%20on%20housing%20affordability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20president%2C%20Biden%20has%20pushed%20a%20series%20of%20pro-housing%20policies%20and%20generally%20favored%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F03%2F21%2Fus%2Fpolitics%2Fbiden-housing-costs.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBiden%2520has%2520seized%2520on%2520the%2Cgoing%2520to%2520wait%252C%25E2%2580%259D%2520Mr.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20federal%20participation%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20housing%20policy.%20Among%20those%20policy%20pushes%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2022%2F05%2F16%2Fpresident-biden-announces-new-actions-to-ease-the-burden-of-housing-costs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BHousing%20Supply%20Action%26quot%3B%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20leverages%20federal%20grants%20and%20loans%20to%20incentivize%20states%20and%20cities%20to%20loosen%20land%20use%20regulations%20and%20facilitate%20new%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3