July%2016%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20statement%20comes%20after%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%20citing%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%2C%20reported%20that%20Musk%20plans%20to%20give%20USD%2045%20million%20a%20month%20to%20a%20new%20super%20political-action%20committee%20supporting%20Trump's%20presidential%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerica%20PAC%2C%20formed%20in%20June%2C%20is%20focused%20on%20registering%20voters%20and%20urging%20constituents%20to%20vote%20early%20and%20request%20mail-in%20ballots%20in%20swing%20states%2C%20according%20to%20one%20of%20the%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20coalition%20assessed%20that%20the%20Democrats%20have%20historically%20had%20very%20robust%20%26quot%3Bget%20out%20the%20vote%26quot%3B%20campaigns%20and%20took%20note%20of%20the%20money%20that%20the%20Biden%20camp%20has%20dedicated%20to%20so-called%20on-the-ground%20efforts%20in%20swing%20states.%20America%20PAC%20will%20attempt%20to%20counter%20that%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20Street.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20Musk%20is%20the%20world's%20richest%20person%2C%20with%20an%20estimated%20fortune%20of%20more%20than%20USD%20250%20billion.%20For%20its%20efforts%2C%20America%20PAC%20has%20hired%20a%20number%20of%20employees%20and%20has%20been%20registering%20voters%2C%20holding%20discussions%20with%20constituents%20in%20swing%20states%20and%20urging%20voters%20to%20request%20mail-in%20ballots%2C%20according%20to%20some%20of%20the%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20filing%20made%20on%20Monday%2C%20America%20PAC%20had%20USD%208.75%20million%20in%20contributions%20for%20the%20three-month%20duration%2C%20which%20ended%20on%20June%2030%2C%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20March%2C%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20intend%20to%20make%20d