ding%20ceremony%20and%20a%20separate%20Hindu%20ceremony%20conducted%20by%20a%20Hindu%20priest%2C%20honouring%20Usha's%20Hindu%20heritage.%20They%20have%20three%20children%20-%20Ewan%2C%206%2C%20Vivek%2C%204%2C%20and%20Mirabel%2C%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%2C%20reflecting%20on%20her%20upbringing%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Breligious%20household%26quot%3B%2C%20attributed%20her%20support%20for%20Vance's%20religious%20journey%20to%20her%20parents'%20influence.%20%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20are%20Hindu%20and%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20made%20them%20such%20good%20parents%20and%20good%20people.%20And%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20power%20of%20that%20in%20my%20own%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Usha.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20knew%20that%20JD%20was%20searching%20for%20something.%20This%20just%20felt%20right%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20parents'%20Hindu%20faith%20made%20them%20great%20parents%E2%80%9D%20-%20Usha%20Vance%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe's%20a%20Hindu%20%26amp%3B%20was%20supportive%20of%20her%20husband's%20rediscovery%20of%20his%20own%20faith%20(One%20of%20her%20sons%20is%20named%20Vivek%20too%20%3F%3F%3F%3F)%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnVance%2C%20anti-war%20%26amp%3B%20Trump's%20VP%2C%20so%20far%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20net%20positive%20for%20India%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKtbOUNT9ba%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKtbOUNT9ba%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Alexei%20Arora%20(%40AlexeiArora)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAlexeiArora%2Fstatus%2F1812939370523160971%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20they%20raise%20their%20children%2C%20given%20their%20different%20religious%20backgrounds%2C%20Usha%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20communication.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20talk%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20stating%20there%20are%20certain%20values%20and%20principles%20that%20she%20and%20Vance%20%26quot%3Bsimply%20agree%20on%26quot%3B%20family%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%20Chilukuri%20Vance%20is%20a%20lawyer%2C%20as%20per%20her%20LinkedIn%20profile.%20She%20was%20raised%20in%20a%20San%20Diego%20suburb%20and%20attended%20Mt.%20Carmel%20High%20School.%20She%20graduated%20with%20a%20BA%20in%20history%20from%20Yale%20University%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20pursued%20further%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20earning%20an%20MPhil%20in%202009%20as%20a%20Gates%20Cambridge%20Scholar.%20She%20worked%20as%20an%20associate%20at%20Munger%2C%20Tolles%20%26amp%3B%20Olson%20LLP.%20She%20was%20a%20Law%20Clerk%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20the%20US%20and%20the%20US%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20for%20the%20District%20of%20Columbia%20Circuit.%20She%20also%20worked%20as%20a%20Summer%20Associate%20at%20Taft%20Stettinius%20%26amp%3B%20Hollister%20LLP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJD%20Vance%20has%20often%20credited%20Usha%20for%20her%20support%20in%20his%20success.%20During%20a%202020%20interview%20with%20The%20Megyn%20Kelly%20Show%2C%20Vance%20described%20his%20wife%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpowerful%20female%20voice%26quot%3B%20guiding%20him.%20%26quot%3BUsha%20definitely%20brings%20me%20back%20to%20earth.%20If%20I%20get%20a%20little%20too%20cocky%20or%20a%20little%20too%20proud%2C%20I%20remind%20myself%20that%20she's%20way%20more%20accomplished%20than%20I%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20back%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721119020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fjpavgc2_jd-vance_625x300_16_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-jd-vances-wife-usha-vance-said-about-her-hindu-upbringing-its-influence-on-life-6116180%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%2C%20Usha%20Vance%20talked%20about%20her%20upbringing%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Breligi