to%20ensure%20that%20the%20couple's%20six-year-old%20child%20is%20taken%20care%20off%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20that%20the%20husband%20will%20serve%20his%20sentence%20first%20and%20after%20he%20completes%20his%20term%2C%20the%20woman%20is%20to%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20arrangement%20shall%20not%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20precedent%20as%20it%20was%20ordered%20in%20these%20special%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20top%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20woman's%20first%20husband%20challenging%20a%20Madras%20High%20Court%20order%20that%20had%20sentenced%20the%20couple%20for%20just%20a%20day%20till%20the%20%26quot%3Brising%20of%20the%20court%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20court%20said%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bflea-bite%20sentence%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Madras%20High%20Court%20was%20inadequate%20for%20a%20serious%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20matter%20of%20awarding%20sentence%20for%20conviction%20of%20an%20offence%20which%20may%20impact%20the%20society%2C%20it%20is%20not%20advisable%20to%20let%20off%20an%20accused%20after%20conviction%20with%20a%20flea-bite%20sentence%20...%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20exceptional%20circumstances%2C%20%5BCourts%20must%5D%20impose%20sentence%20in%20tune%20with%20the%20rule%20of%20proportionality%20in%20providing%20punishment%20though%20it%20falls%20within%20the%20realm%20of%20judicial%20discretion.%26quot%3B%20it%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721115360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Far9jdb9g_supreme-court_625x300_13_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbigamy-supreme-court-second-marriage-alternate-prison-time-awarded-to-couple-accused-of-bigamy-for-childs-care-6116482%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20yesterday%20sentenced%20a%20woman%20and%20her%20second%20husband%20to%20six%20months%20in