2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111776075.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVicky%20Kaushal%20has%20dropped%20the%20most%20romantic%20birthday%20post%20for%20Katrina%20Kaif%20and%20the%20internet%20cannot%20wait%20to%20see%20them%20together%20in%20a%20movie!%20Vicky%20has%20shared%20some%20unseen%20pictures%20which%20are%20winning%20the%20internet!%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsquishy-hugs-to-bonding-over-pizza-vicky-kaushals-birthday-wish-for-katrina-is-all-things-love-netizens-cant-keep-calm-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F111776075.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20AI%20Chip%20In%20Development%20May%20Revolutionise%20ChatGPT%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20why%20you%20are%20able%20to%20ask%20ChatGPT%20%26quot%3Bhow%20to%20eat%20a%20mango%20without%20spilling%20it%26quot%3B%20and%20much%20more%20is%20Nvidia's%20H100%20and%20B200%20Graphics%20Processing%20Units%20(GPUs).%20These%20magical%20chipsets%20that%20power%20AI%20chatbots%20have%20propelled%20Nvidia%20to%20become%20the%20frontrunners%20of%20the%20AI%20hardware%20industry%2C%20with%20market%20capitalization%20reaching%20the%203%20trillion-dollar%20mark-more%20than%20Microsoft%20and%20Apple%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20a%20relatively%20young%20startup%20founded%20by%20two%20Harvard%20dropouts%20have%20set%20their%20eyes%20on%20their%20share%20of%20the%20AI%20hardware%20pie.%20Etched%2C%20the%20California%20based%20startup%2C%20is%20looking%20to%20disrupt%20the%20AI%20chipset%20market%20with%20their%20transformer%20ASIC%20(Application%20Specific%20Integrated%20Circuits)%20chip%20called%20Sohu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESohu%20claims%20to%20be%2020%20times%20faster%20in%20running%20transformers%20like%20ChatGPT%20than%20Nvidia's%20flagship-%20H100.%20The%20B200%2C%20which%20is%20the%20more%20powerful%20Nvidia%20offering%20than%20H100%2C%20is%20reportedly%2010%20times%20slower%20then%20Sohu%2C%20according%20to%20the%20claims%20made%20by%20the%20company%20based%20on%20emulation%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Source%3A%20X%2F%40Etched%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Source%3A%20X%2F%40Etched%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fmfs4l3n8_etched-ai-chip_625x300_16_July_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESource%3A%20X%2F%40Etched%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESohu%20is%20taking%20an%20entirely%20different%20approach%20to%20providing%20high%20computational%20power%20to%20run%20billions%20of%20parameters%20(Variables%20that%20are%20used%20in%20training%20an%20AI%20Model)%20for%20transformer%20models.%20Unlike%20GPUs%20that%20can%20do%20multiple%20computationally%20heavy%20tasks%20(like%20rendering%20graphics%20in%20real%20time)%2C%20Etched%20is%20choosing%20to%20create%20a%20specialised%20chip%20that%20caters%20to%20only%20transformer%20AI%20models%20-%20ones%20that%20run%20ChatGPT%2C%20Sora%20(OpenAI's%20text%20to%20video%20AI%20model)%20and%20Google's%20Gemini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20this%20means%20is%20it%20cannot%20run%20other%20AI%20models%20like%20Convolutional%20Neural%20Networks%20(used%20for%20image%20recognition).%20This%20opens%20up%20the%20possibility%20of%20exploring%20new%20AI%20products%20by%20developers%20that%20were%20till%20now%20not%20possible%20due%20to%20limited%20power%20on%20GPUs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20Sohu%20can%20potentially%20lead%20to%20a%20real-time%20translator%20that%20can%20hear%20and%20read%20Hindi%2C%20Gujarati%20or%20Tamil%20and%20respond%20back%20in%20French%2C%20English%20and%20German.%20Of%20course%2C%20such%20multimodal%20and%20multilingual%20translation%20needs%20more%20than%20just%20the%20computational%20power%2C%20but%20in%20theory%2C%20it%20opens%20up%20the%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20multimodal%20application%20of%20transformers%20that%20the%20chipset%20might%20tap%20into%20is%20integrating%20visual%20and%20language%20areas.%20This%20essentially%20means%20that%20such%20a%20model%20will%20understand%20both%20text%20and%20images%20simultaneously%2C%20throwing%20open%20the%20possibility%20of%20visual%20questions%20and%20answers-%20like%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20of%20this%20remains%20a%20theory.%20Etched%20has%20raised%20120%20million%20USD%20on%2025%20June%20to%20make%20it%20a%20reality%2C%20with%20a%20real%20timeline%20as%20to%20an%20actual%20release%20of%20the%20Sohu%20ASIC%20remaining%20elusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday%20we%20announced%20our%20%24120M%20fundraise%20to%20bring%20Sohu%20to%20the%20world.%20Thanks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEdLudlow%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40edludlow%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20hosting%20us!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkhzMPAofng%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FkhzMPAofng%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FQ4SeuUjP2h%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FQ4SeuUjP2h%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Etched%20(%40Etched)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEtched%2Fstatus%2F1805775989500428739%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2026%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EEtched%20has%20claimed%20it%20already%20has%20%26quot%3Btens%20of%20million%20dollars%26quot%3B%20worth%20of%20hardware%20reserved%20in%20preorders.%20The%20company%20has%20also%20secured%20a%20deal%20with%20TSMC%20(Taiwan%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Company)%20to%20fabricate%20the%204-nanometer%20chip%2C%20promising%20the%20deal%20is%20going%20to%20help%20%26quot%3Bramp%20up%20our%20first%20year%20of%20production.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published