ack%20to%20the%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shilpa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20Suneet%2C%20who%20was%20always%20interested%20in%20reducing%20their%20energy%20footprint%20and%20adopting%20sustainable%20manners%20of%20living%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20wife%20encouraged%20me%20to%20be%20enthused%20and%20come%20up%20with%20solutions%20where%20we%20did%20not%20compromise%20on%20our%20quality%20and%20standard%20of%20living.%20Otherwise%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20very%20easy%20to%20cut%20down%20on%20this%20and%20be%20sustainable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20decided%20to%20go%20off-grid.%20%E2%80%9CNormally%2C%20people%20believe%20that%20large%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Fsolar-powered-homes-of-india-rooftop-panels-save-electricity-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20PV%20installations%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecan%20only%20be%20done%20for%20farmhouses.%20We%20wanted%20to%20prove%20that%20we%20can%20lead%20sustainable%20lives%20even%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20bustling%20city%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shilpa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20moving%20to%20the%20bungalow%2C%20the%20couple%20installed%2042%20panels%20of%202%C3%971%20metres%20each%2C%20spread%20across%2021%20sq%20m%20of%20the%20terrace.%20While%20the%20installation%20took%20two%20weeks%2C%20building%20the%20whole%20electronics%20took%20them%20about%20eight%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1720701178.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20Shilpa%20and%20Suneet%2C%20the%20first%20biggest%20transformation%20with%20this%20setup%20was%20to%20have%20an%20uninterrupted%20power%20supply.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1720701178.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1720701178-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1720701178-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1720701178-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-1720701178-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356495%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20Shilpa%20and%20Suneet%2C%20the%20first%20biggest%20transformation%20with%20this%20setup%20was%20to%20have%20an%20uninterrupted%20power%20supply.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20grid-backed%20setfup%20was%20different%20from%20a%20net-metered%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20two%2C%20Suneet%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20net-metered%20system%2C%20you%20do%20not%20require%20to%20store%20the%20energy%20and%20feed%20excess%20energy%20to%20the%20grid%20and%20get%20it%20back%20from%20it%20when%20you%20are%20not%20generating%20enough%20power.%20It%20is%20a%20more%20economical%20way%20for%20harnessing%20solar%20energy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20grid-backed%20setup%2C%20we%20do%20not%20feed%20excess%20power%20to%20the%20grid%2C%20we%20instead%20store%20the%20excess%20energy%20and%20use%20it%20during%20non-generation%20hours%2C%20say%20during%20the%20nights%20and%20cloudy%20days.%20We%20have%20our%20own%20backup.%20As%20long%20as%20I%20am%20dependent%20on%20the%20grid%2C%20we%20are%20responsible%20for%20coal-backed%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20major%20production%20of%20electricity%20is%20achieved%20through%20coal%20thermal%20power%20plants%20which%20is%20around%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2