otecting%20our%20forests%20and%20supporting%20the%20community.%20With%20the%20growing%20impact%20of%20climate%20change%20and%20heightened%20focus%20on%20environmental%20issues%2C%20I%20realised%20there%20are%20many%20opportunities%20for%20meaningful%20work%20in%20this%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20realisation%20sparked%20my%20interest%20in%20the%20service%2C%20and%20it%20was%20then%20that%20I%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20exam%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20this%2C%20Harsimran%20had%20already%20attempted%20the%20Union%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20Civil%20Services%20Examinations%20(UPSC%20CSE)%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F353815%2Fias-officer-ashish-kumar-singhal-jaipur-cleared-upsc-cse-after-four-failures-topper%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20times%20without%20success%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20also%20approaching%20the%20age%20of%2032%2C%20the%20maximum%20limit%20for%20a%20general%20candidate%20in%20the%20UPSC.%20I%20wanted%20to%20give%20it%20one%20last%20try%20since%20I%20had%20nothing%20to%20lose%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harsimran%2C%20who%20was%20then%20working%20as%20the%20Inspector%20of%20Cooperative%20Society%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20multiple%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F327369%2Fagra-ifs-officer-pawan-gupta-shares-how-to-crack-upsc-after-failed-attempts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efailed%20attempts%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20UPSC%20CSE%2C%20Harsimran%20finally%20achieved%20a%20remarkable%20feat%20on%20his%20first%20attempt%20in%20the%20UPSC%20IFS%20(Indian%20Forest%20Service)%20examination%20in%202022%2C%20securing%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2016%20on%20his%20first%20attempt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201