with%20spices%20and%20a%20generous%20dollop%20of%20%3Cem%3Eghee%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20then%20why%20does%20my%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20never%20measure%20up%20to%20those%20made%20by%20the%20stalwarts%20of%20the%20household%3F%20Some%20might%20attribute%20it%20to%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Emaa%20ka%20pyaar%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(mother%E2%80%99s%20love)%2C%20and%20while%20that%20sentiment%20holds%20true%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20also%20a%20scientific%20aspect%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrish%20Ashok%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20unravel%20this%20science%20and%20share%20it%20with%20the%20world.%20When%20he%20moved%20to%20the%20US%20for%20work%2C%20he%20discovered%20that%20his%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20potato%20fry%20far%20outshone%20his%20own.%20How%20does%20one%20achieve%20that%20elusive%20perfect%20crispness%3F%20Why%20do%20you%20add%20some%20spices%20after%20others%20and%20roast%20them%20for%20lesser%20times%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20because%20the%20recipe%20book%20says%20so.%20It%E2%80%99s%20due%20to%20chemical%20reactions%20that%20occur.%20The%20search%20behind%20these%20reasons%20led%20to%20Ashok%E2%80%99s%20journey%20towards%20becoming%20a%20kitchen%20alchemist!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20780px)%20100vw%2C%20780px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashok%20with%20his%20parents%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628.jpg%20780w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-300x197.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-500x328.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fkrish-ashok-1720529628-768x504.jpg%2076