e%2C%20the%20school%20had%20a%20new%20headmaster%20who%20conducted%20extra%20classes%20and%20solved%20doubts%2C%20helping%20her%20clear%20class%2010%20with%20flying%20colours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20palm%20tapping%20was%20banned%20in%20Namakkal%2C%20which%20meant%20an%20even%20meagre%20income%20for%20the%20family.%20Her%20mother%20fell%20sick%2C%20which%20drove%20Sudha%20to%20work%20before%20and%20after%20school.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20go%20to%20the%20sugarcane%20fields%20before%20school%20and%20do%20any%20work%20that%20came%20my%20way%20as%20our%20situation%20was%20dire.%20After%20that%2C%20I%20cycled%20to%20school.%20My%20evenings%20were%20similar.%20I%20would%20then%20sell%20the%20sugarcane%2C%20which%20greatly%20helped%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20class%2012%2C%20she%20studied%20BSc%20while%20working.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20wanted%20at%20least%20one%20of%20us%20to%20study%20ahead.%20She%20said%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducation%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20grow%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20life.%20I%2C%20too%2C%20am%20a%20strong%20believer%20in%20the%20same.%20It%20is%20a%20tool%20to%20move%20ahead%20in%20life%20and%20to%20achieve%20economic%20freedom%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20her%20sister%20got%20married%20and%20Sudha%20had%20two%20choices%20%E2%80%94%20opt%20for%20higher%20studies%20or%20get%20married%20herself.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20no-brainer%20that%20Sudha%20chose%20the%20former%20by%20trading%20the%20money%20for%20her%20marriage%20for%20her%20BEd%20and%20MSc.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EStarting%20a%20business%20with%20Rs%202%2C000%3C